title: NFL Week 12 Recap (Football 11/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the week that was in the NFL during Week 12. The guys talk about the Browns-Bengals (1:00), Steelers-Broncos (10:00), Ravens-Raiders (20:45), Packers-Vikings (27:30), Colts-Dolphins (37:00), Bills-Jaguars (42:00), Eagles-Giants (48:15), Jets-Patriots (50:00), Chargers-Cardinals (53:55), 49ers-Buccaneers (55:10), Sean's Game of Thrones Monopoly board (1:00) and Panthers-Seahawks (1:08).
